In brief, plants were grown from seeds in environmental chambers (Hühren Kälte-Klima-Elektrotechnik, Erkelenz, Germany), equipped with metal halide lamps (Philips, Hamburg, Germany), following the protocol described in Junker-Frohn et al. (2019), under controlled conditions of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
