In total, we found an up-regulation of structural genes involved in the flavonoid and anthocyanidin biosynthesis in both species 4 and 7 days after stress treatment. In addition, the expression of structural genes is often higher induced after 7 days when compared with day 4. The induced expression of genes involved in the production of flavonoids is more pronounced for the cultivated tomato than in the wild relative (genes \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
